ing committed to Interact and I\'ll see you at our first meeting!!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Meeting dates:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>First meeting: Sept 15th\r\n<li>                       Sept 29th\r\n<li>                       October 6th\r\n<li>                       October 20th\r\n<li>                       November 3rd\r\n<li>                       November 10th\r\n<li>                       December 1st\r\n<li>                       December 8th\r\n<li>                        January 5th\r\n<li>                        January 26th\r\n<li>                        February 9th\r\n<li>                        February 23rd\r\n<li>                        March 8th\r\n<li>                        March 22nd\r\n<li>                        April 19th\r\n<li>                        April 26th\r\n<li>                        May 3rd\r\n<li>                        May 17th\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Please let me know if you have any questions.<br>\r\n\r\nMiss Paxton</p>','2011-09-06 14:00:01','inactive','2011-09-20 16:44:27','25'),(166,'index.php','OtherStuff','','<h2>Monthly New Letters From The District Governor</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.clubrunner.ca/Data/5450/HTML/132622/0711-DISTRICT_NL_JULY_2011.pdf\">July 2011 News Letter</a></li>\r\n<li><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://campaign.r20.constantcontact.com/render?llr=6zi9qpcab&v=001nphfS6MPjGkb4DImOLf-I6kmWZKQL1bNV6sgRHvEYrqlbws6PN_f3XmFhOfzdkIOZ_AvSOas2XWEb11Yq7hsRYJGP92Au7w1odwBnoS7nJSGaspZEcJsQFKbIjlBzzt9TV7HsomWEuyK0ooaefS41hYbpjagzC3mmnzXipeD0gFUwefYiKno7tNeDvLW17Hre2L8oH9bxkWS7F4V37aT3Q%3D%3D\">August 2011 News Letter</a></li>\r\n<li><a target=_blank\" href=\"http://campaign.r20.constantcontact.com/render?llr=6zi9qpcab&v=0013-zw4rcnoTtwZ-R2hWOktrFMuwX_8j7I8ctEsZXTUVreNIUqwsPdClIMjpRVAPzlw6nXMuVRtv7OgNKYlHUpPZq8emtpZb-ga-uD2qN6Z0oGgxGUjACkUpNU_CRAQ7IrZy3ikZFp1pat01OzFC_eiauc5AO5wBS3BCooS8sitPHR94Ui0BfrVRiHj4s8SCmViy36Kayg7pa7rM7fJsQCeQ%3D%3D\">September 2011 News Letter</a></li>\r\n</ul>','2011-09-07 16:06:59','inactive','2011-10-13 17:05:08','25'),(167,'meetings.php','Message','Speaker Suggestions','<p>If you are having trouble finding a speaker we have a list of several possible speakers:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Dave Lively\'s from the Grand Co Historical Assoc: 970-725-3939. gchadirector@rkymtnhi.com, dclively@netzero.com</li>\r\n<li>Mary Entrican River View Counseling: PO Box 678, Kremmling CO 80459, (970)531-1996, mary@riverviewcounseling.com</li>\r\n<li>Jeff Verosky:<br>\r\nI emailed Jeff and here is his answer:<br>\r\nI would be happy to come and speak about our great school. I am free most Wednesday\'s, but if you send me some of your dates, I can see if my schedule would fit. Also, if there is anything specific you would like me to speak about, I would be happy to do that. Or I can speak about an overview of the programs we offer kids and use to help our students meet adequate yearly growth or more.\r\n<br>\r\nJeff Verosky <a href=\"mailto:jversoky@egsd.org\">jverosky@egsd.org</a><br>\r\nPrincipal<br>\r\nEast Grand Middle School<br>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>Jane Harmon:<br>\r\nI emailed Jane and here is her answer:<br>\r\nI would be happy to do so. My phone is 887-2104 or 970-629-8699 or my <a href=\"mailto:jharmon@egsd.org\">email</a> is the best way to contact me. I would need notice of a week or so to make this work most likely.<br>\r\nJane\r\n</li>\r\n<li>Erika Iverson<br>I am from a local non-profit, Grand Futures Prevention Coalition. I was wondering about opportunities to present at Rotary’s Board Meetings on our organization and how we work in the community. Our mission is to create and support heath, positive lifestyles choices as alternatives to substance abuse in our community.<br>\r\nThank you,<br>\r\nErika Iverson<br>\r\nerika iverson, mph<br>\r\ngrand county director<br>\r\ngrand futures prevention coalition<br>\r\nerika@grandfutures.org<br>\r\n970-887-9655\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>If you don\'t have a talk or a speaker yet please contact one of the above people.</p>\r\n\r\n','2011-09-08 11:07:42','inactive','2012-03-30 18:01:29','25'),(168,'index.php','OtherStuff','','<h2>Monthly New Letters From The District Governor</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.clubrunner.ca/Data/5450/HTML/132622/0711-DISTRICT_NL_JULY_2011.pdf\">July 2011 News Letter</a></li>\r\n<li><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://campaign.r20.constantcontact.com/render?llr=6zi9qpcab&v=001nphfS6MPjGkb4DImOLf-I6kmWZKQL1bNV6sgRHvEYrqlbws6PN_f3XmFhOfzdkIOZ_AvSOas2XWEb11Yq7hsRYJGP92Au7w1odwBnoS7nJSGaspZEcJsQFKbIjlBzzt9TV7HsomWEuyK0ooaefS41hYbpjagzC3mmnzXipeD0gFUwefYiKno7tNeDvLW17Hre2L8oH9bxkWS7F4V37aT3Q%3D%3D\">August 2011 News Letter</a></li>\r\n<li><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://campaign.r20.constantcontact.com/render?llr=6zi9qpcab&v=0013-zw4rcnoTtwZ-R2hWOktrFMuwX_8j7I8ctEsZXTUVreNIUqwsPdClIMjpRVAPzlw6nXMuVRtv7OgNKYlHUpPZq8emtpZb-ga-uD2qN6Z0oGgxGUjACkUpNU_CRAQ7IrZy3ikZFp1pat01OzFC_eiauc5AO5wBS3BCooS8sitPHR94Ui0BfrVRiHj4s8SCmViy36Kayg7pa7rM7fJsQCeQ%3D%3D\">September 2011 News Letter</a></li>\r\n<li><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://campaign.r20.constantcontact.com/render?llr=6zi9qpcab&v=001EbGq4AQcELQn9yQE0rz3NhIYqpgJ7O7Z-2YCPHXDj17R4Jqy8Uh_yJuoVFpFjdtGmnAhKJFxCpeO3P3fWEtFFuRkRvIIB2aqu2ctqiHVHjrXcRnS8mNh5Ic_-NvB83raISmM6HYOtYiC1-WWo_lJ9-nKn0EwfceK2tozGdVLf9RWa1gBeClXCl82K2p10B31P-j62q8ipYEbGXf03NenjQ%3D%3D\">October 2011 News Letter</a></li>\r\n</ul>','2011-10-13 10:05:08','inactive','2011-11-16 20:30:29','25'),(169,'index.php','OtherStuff','','<h2>Monthly New Letters From The District Governor</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.clubrunner.ca/Data/5450/HTML/132622/0711-DISTRICT_NL_JULY_2011.pdf\">July 2011 News Letter</a></li>\r\n<li><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://campaign.r20.constantcontact.com/render?llr=6zi9qpcab&v=001nphfS6MPjGkb4DImOLf-I6kmWZKQL1bNV6sgRHvEYrqlbws6PN_f3XmFhOfzdkIOZ_AvSOas2XWEb11Yq7hsRYJGP92Au7w1odwBnoS7nJSGaspZEcJsQFKbIjlBzzt9TV7HsomWEuyK0ooaefS41hYbpjagzC3mmnzXipeD0gFUwefYiKno7tNeDv